Author's Note: Response to a sort-of fic challenge from SamAndJack4Ever. Has to include a reference to a horrible and painful death for Brumby, and have Harm and Mac shippiness guaranteed. If you just love Brumby and can't bear the thought of losing him, please don't read this, because you'll get very mad at me. Also, kind of an anything can happen ending, but no sequel planned (yet).<br>
